# CODEOWNERS file
# 
# This file defines code ownership for automatic reviewer assignment.
# Each line is a file pattern followed by one or more owners.
# 
# Owners can be:
# - @username (GitHub username)
# - @org/team-name (GitHub team)
# - email@example.com (email address)
#
# More information: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owners for everything in the repo
# Will be requested for review when someone opens a pull request
